com.github.bwsoft.iris.message.sbe

Class SBEField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bwsoft.iris.message.sbe.SBEField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Field, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SBEMessage

    public class SBEField
extends java.lang.Object
implements Field
    The base class for all fields in a SBE message. It extends the basic Field by adding a couple of additional operations that are specific to SBE message.
    Author:
    yzhou
